Nintendo Switches are selling out—here’s where you can still buy oneYou can still find the Nintendo Switch and Switch Lite online.
With the release of Animal Crossing New Horizons and most of us looking for something to entertain us, it seems like everyone and their mother are trying to buy a Nintendo Switch.
Thankfully, you can still find the Nintendo Switch Lite (the Switch's cheaper cousin) at a few reliable retailers, though you may have to wait several days to have it shipped to your door.
To help you get your game on, we've rounded up all the retailers where you can find the Nintendo Switch and Nintendo Switch Lite, and will continue to update this as the consoles go in and out of stock.
